snippet: A video circulating online Sunday showed gleeful trespassers diving off a balcony into a pool in the residential compound abandoned by the American Embassy when it pulled out of Tripoli in July.
abstract: Libyans overrun residential compound abandoned when United States Embassy compound was evacuated in July; no evidence has emerged that embassy itself has been overrun.

byline.contributor: Suliman Ali Zway contributed reporting from Tripoli, Libya.

lead_paragraph: A video circulating online Sunday showed gleeful trespassers diving off a balcony into a pool in the residential compound abandoned by the American Embassy when it pulled out of Tripoli in July.

headline.main: Libyans Overrun Compound Abandoned by U.S. Embassy in Tripoli
headline.print_headline: Libyans Overrun Residential Compound Abandoned by U.S. Embassy in July
